You will never be FORGOTTEN!! \\m/
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:
This mod contains a big range of different spandex
models with extreme metal bands!
It can be forged at any forge in the leather category.
It\'s ONLY avaiable for max weight. ;)

Location:
It is located in Whiterun. When you enter look to the right and go into the small tunnel.
Then again right and you will find them.

Installation:
As usual drop all the files into your ...\\Skyrim\\Data ordner.

Deinstallation:
Delete the installed files from your ...\\Skyrim\\Data ordner.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Versions:
1.0 - 140 Models in 2 chests added to the game
1.1 - Added 10 new models; 5 in every chest
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Big Thanks to: 
Caliente for his Big Bottom edition CBBE (Required)
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2666
SourandSweet for his spandex model!
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/20009
